# Directory structure

Next.js 16 app root. Product docs: `project.md`. Agent hints: `AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md`.

## Top-level

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/` | App UI, API routes, shared lib and types |
| `scripts/` | CLI: sync cotações (BR/US), job progress, `env` loading |
| `db/supabase/` | SQL DDL (run in Supabase) — ativos, aportes, cotacoes, status_cron_job |
| `dev/` | Internal notes, plans, scratch (not app runtime) |
| `public/` | Static assets (SVGs, etc.) |
| `.cursor/rules/` | Cursor rules (`.mdc`) |
| `.vscode/` | Editor settings |

## Config (root)

`package.json` / `package-lock.json`, `tsconfig.json`, `next.config.ts`, `next-env.d.ts`, `postcss.config.mjs`, `eslint.config.mjs`, `.gitignore`. Secrets: `.env.local` (gitignored).

## `src/`

```
src/
├── app/                    # App Router
│   ├── layout.tsx, page.tsx, globals.css, favicon.ico
│   ├── cadastro-ativos/, listagem-ativos/
│   ├── cadastro-aportes/, listagem-aportes/
│   ├── cache/
│   └── api/                # Route handlers (see api-routes.mdc)
│       ├── quote/
│       ├── assets/, assets/[id]/
│       ├── aportes/, aportes/[id]/, aportes/check/
│       └── cache/status/, cache/trigger/
├── components/             # e.g. Navbar
├── lib/                    # supabase, brapi-service, twelvedata-service, constants
└── types/                  # Shared TS models (aporte, asset, brapi, cotacao, cron-job)
```

## `scripts/`

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `env.ts` | Load env for tsx CLIs |
| `sync-cotacoes.ts` | Brapi batch — ativos `acao` / `fii` |
| `sync-cotacoes-us.ts` | Twelve Data — `stock` / `reit` |
| `job-progress.ts` | Updates `status_cron_job` when run with job id |

## `db/supabase/`

`create_table_ativos.sql`, `create_table_aportes.sql`, `create_table_cotacoes.sql`, `create_table_status_cron_job.sql`.

## Related rules

- `project-conventions.mdc` — stack, pt-BR, env, design tokens
